When the ion telescopes viewed the sunlit Earth, the front detectors saturated and the fluxes would drop to zero. This would typically occur at low L\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
